{"type":"message","id":"f4960c44","parentId":"c255e5fb","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:56:03.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我是 The ONE Project 的 AI 总管，Andy。作为你的全职个人管家，我负责协调所有 AI 代理团队、管理三大支柱（价值50% + 专业30% + 梦想20%），并确保 everything aligns with 你的巴菲特式价值投资哲学和勇敢专注的生活原则。\n\n简单说：我是你在这个 AI 世界里的最高代表。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":15463,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15546,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772268959115}}
