{"type":"message","id":"90fc77af","parentId":"6fa3d534","timestamp":"2026-02-28T10:58:53.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我找到了根本问题！从配置中可以看出：\n\n**问题根源：**\n1. **心跳任务的目标 chat ID 错误** - 配置中 `agents.defaults.heartbeat.to` 和 `agents.list.stock.heartbeat.to` 都设置为 `-1003661163902`（群组ID）\n2. **但你的私聊消息来自 `5520269161`** - 这是你的个人 Telegram ID\n3. **心跳任务尝试向群组发送消息，但你是在私聊中与各代理对话**\n\n**具体分析：**\n- Coordinator Heartbeat 任务配置为向群组 `-1003661163902` 发送\n- 但你在私聊中与 coding/stock 等代理对话（chat_id: `5520269161`）\n- 当心跳任务执行时，它尝试向群组发送健康检查，但可能群组中没有正确配置或 bot 没有权限\n- 这导致了 \"chat not found\" 错误，进而使任务被标记为 \"disabled\"\n\n**解决方案：**\n需要将心跳任务的目标从群组ID改为你的个人ID `5520269161`。\n\n让我修复这个配置问题：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9fdcd38c84d040a686ef9ff4","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","raw":"{\"agents\":{\"defaults\":{\"heartbeat\":{\"to\":\"5520269161\"}},\"list\":[{\"id\":\"main\",\"workspace\":\"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace\"},{\"id\":\"stock\",\"workspace\":\"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace\",\"heartbeat\":{\"every\":\"4h\",\"activeHours\":{\"start\":\"09:30\",\"end\":\"21:30\",\"timezone\":\"America/New_York\"},\"target\":\"telegram\",\"to\":\"5520269161\"}},{\"id\":\"mcs\",\"workspace\":\"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/mcs/workspace\"},{\"id\":\"coding\",\"workspace\":\"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace\"}]}}","note":"修复心跳检测配置：将心跳目标从群组ID改为个人ID 5520269161，解决 \"chat not found\" 错误"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":36479,"output":512,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772276313827}}
